item.title: DJI M600 is a New High-End Drone + Ronin MX for Just $6000 | cinema5D
item.description:
DJI M600 is a New High-End Drone + Ronin MX for Just $6000 | cinema5D

The newly introduced DJI Matrice 600 is a very competitively priced new hexacopter that integrates seamlessly with the Ronin-MX, an upgraded version of DJI's 3-axis gimbal Ronin-M. Just unveiled at NAB, the gimbal includes all the functionality of previous Ronin incarnations, as well as a built in receiver and remote control.
